{"word":"λίκνον","slug":"λίκνον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n63263\" key=\"li/knon\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λίκνον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen> (also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λεῖκνον</foreign> acc. to Hdn.Gr.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg3136.tlg001:2:543\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.543</biblScope></bibl>, and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λικμός</foreign> (q.v.)), <sense id=\"n63263.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">winnowing-fan</tr_>, i.e. a broad basket, in which the corn was placed after threshing, and then thrown against the wind so as to winnow the grain from the chaff, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg026:368b:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mete.\">Mete.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">368b29</biblScope> </bibl>; sacred to Dionysus, and carried on the head at his festivals, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.165</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phal.\">Phal.</a></author> </bibl>); also to Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg008.perseus-grc1:844\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">844</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λικνίτης, λικνοφόρος</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n63263.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cradle,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">h.Merc.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.150</biblScope></bibl>, al., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg002:48\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Jov.\">Jov.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:268\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">268</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.37</biblScope></bibl>, etc.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}